Module core.java.datamodel
Package com.pineframework.core.datamodel.model

Class FlatTransient<I extends Serializable>

java.lang.Object
com.pineframework.core.datamodel.model.FlatTransient<I>
Type Parameters:
I - the type of identity
All Implemented Interfaces:
Transient<I>, Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
EmptyModel, TreeTransient
public abstract class FlatTransient<I extends Serializable> extends Object implements Transient<I>
All models such as value objects, data transfer object (DTO), etc should be extended from AbstractTransient. FlatTransient implements equals and hash code and also toString method.
